{"tid":1658972,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「重要長文」所有和理非係遊行之前都必須要搞清楚一件事","createTime":"2019-10-16T17:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T14:45:29.000Z","uid":229380,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d733665acf02925d8e554d1cd416dc8f9b763b","tid":1658972,"uid":229380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:01:48.000Z","msg":"好多人都搞錯咗一樣嘢，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不被捕</strong></span>唔係要「小心」「注意」<br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>首要任務</strong></span>，去到而家仲係好多人都唔明不被捕嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重要性</span></strong>。<br />\n你只要答我呢條問題就會明，<br />\n上周末有二百幾個手足被捕，<span style=\"color: red;\">咁義務律師又有幾多人？</span><br />\n黑警雖然係人渣，但佢地唔蠢。<br />\n每次係大型示威之後，佢哋一定奉旨濫捕，目的就係為左分散義務律師既人手，令佢地疲於奔命。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲可以方便虐待示威者</span><br />\n唔俾飲水<br />\n唔俾食嘢<br />\n唔俾去廁所<br />\n唔俾治療<br />\n仲可以大條道理話，被捕人士眾多<br />\n<br />\n佢哋要打死一個示威者，衹要拉多十幾廿個唔關事嘅普通人，就唔會有人仲有精力留意到個位手足<br />\n<br />\n<ins>只要你不被捕，咁樣前線被捕既手足，分到既資源就會更多，就會有更多人關注到佢哋嘅人身安全。</ins><br />\n<br />\n坦白説，近幾次大型示威，其實基本上六、七點前已經差唔多散，和理非好心就快D返屋企啦！著住黑衫企喺條街度,其實幫唔到乜嘢,萬一遇到黑警又畀機會佢哋拉你返差館交數，個意義究竟喺邊度。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一開始著黑衫既原因係因為Black Block，但係如果係和理非場合Black Block係咪真係再有用?<br />\n<br />\n<ins>有陣時各位手足只要唔畀人拉已經係一個好開始。</ins><br />\n<br />\n對於今後遊行點樣減少被捕人士，我有少少建議<br />\n<br />\n對於和理非既手足，係和理非大型遊行裏面，真係唔好再著黑衫喇!<br />\n而家場運動已經去到另一個形態喇<br />\n黑色衫嘅意義係一種表態，<br />\n運動早期，前線勇武有好多行動都會擔心失去民意，著黑衫係代表對佢地嘅一種支持，亦可以比社會睇到民意基礎<br />\n但係場運動去到而家，人人都清楚民意已經不可動搖，<br />\n著黑衫只會令我哋成為被黑警針對嘅對象，形成一種我地在明，敵人在暗既形勢<br />\n<br />\n好多淺藍同中立撚，一見到黑衫人畀警察打，就會講「哦~示威者，抵佢啦搞破壞」<br />\n馬上就會表達一種事不關己嘅態度，咁係因為佢哋唔會去遊行，著黑衫<br />\n假如被打嘅人唔係著黑衫，試問呢班自私撚仲會唔會輕鬆話唔關自己事，唔會發生係自己身上？（只要佢地怕黑警就可以，呢D人永遠都唔會成為同路人）<br />\n<br />\n<ins>如果你唔去遊行著黑衫根本意義唔大,<br />\n如果你出得去遊行，咁樣已經係最好表達民意嘅方法,何必執著於黑衫</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於前線勇武手足，<br />\n我建議你哋可以將<ins>十點定位死線，必須撤退<br />\n九點開始，以撤退為大前提行動，只要有機會就儘快退場</ins><br />\n<br />\n點解會有咁既建議有幾個原因<br />\n<br />\n1. 首先而家一般都係18區開花為大前提，分散黑警人手掩護前線，但係同時散場亦都早左，到左夜晚人流明顯少咗，好多人已經去咗食飯或者做其他嘢<br />\n分散黑警人手既效果去到夜晚就會消失，佢地集中返人手就可以計畫大搜捕，上週末就係咁樣俾佢哋捉咗唔少手足<br />\n<br />\n2. 去到夜晚拍片會變得困難，就算有記者在場，一開閃光燈係環境比較昏暗嘅地方根本乜都影唔到，班黑警俾人撚足一日，去到夜晚就係佢哋發洩嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n3. 萬一不幸被捕，晚上幫助你嘅資源同待遇會更小更惡劣<br />\n義務律師、義工可能已經幫緊幾個被捕人士，未必有足夠人手可以搵到你所身處的警署，你將會面對幾個鐘頭甚至更長時間的不人道對待<br />\n<br />\n<ins>撤退嘅時機往往一瞬即逝，當你發覺勢色不對既有時候，可能黑警已經完成咗包圍網<br />\n至於和理非，唔需要替佢地擔心，只要你地一撤，佢地走得快過你地</ins><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得我講嘢有道理麻煩幫手推post"},{"pid":"623c1e62a44ac921e126319b350546a52cb1b2e4","tid":1658972,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"24759d46b5157cf9523fa5f21941cd9a3abbea3f","tid":1658972,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:02:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10 &middot; 20 星期日<br />\n1330 民陣九龍大遊行</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀梳士巴利道花園 -&gt; 高鐵西九龍站<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n提提大家今日有咩活動 (10 &middot; 17)<br />\n<br />\n1. 學界萬人大集會 - 1200<br />\n香港知專設計學院設計大道 HKDI<br />\n<br />\n2. 和你拖2.0 面具人鏈<br />\n - 1900集合 2000開始 2100流水式散去<br />\n港島綫 觀塘綫 荃灣綫 沙田區"},{"pid":"6910dfde9bf4b6a44071c32bda79d1ee7cd5dee5","tid":1658972,"uid":229380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:03:49.000Z","msg":"不被捕,不被捕,不被捕"},{"pid":"dd1e4c3ce65cd0f28c80834514c51f1931ce907d","tid":1658972,"uid":77872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"著黑衫係為左保護前線嘅手足"},{"pid":"63eac00ea06c1cd62836f4fa69fbd72b57db9839","tid":1658972,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:10:11.000Z","msg":"你連點解要blackbloc都唔知"},{"pid":"c76b6e2a3305963fa0a2f7e259f0224108fbe63e","tid":1658972,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:11:54.000Z","msg":"[twitter攻略] 增加大量外國followers<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1658926/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1658926/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5adaa11477b403cdb939f383807c131bcd62c818","tid":1658972,"uid":229380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd1e4c3ce65cd0f28c80834514c51f1931ce907d","tid":1658972,"uid":77872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"著黑衫係為左保護前線嘅手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"如果係保護前線手足,要做澈底black block,<br />\n而唔係淨係著件衫之後周圍企<br />\n我主力講既係和理非回合個時既遊行<br />\n唔想再有手足被針對<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a6323fbc0387bd91104ee09f3cbd0be545bdab","tid":1658972,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894994d8aea6a5cdbbd372cca7d3b1008a468074","tid":1658972,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d91ba8f966472410e00115c0cc2c1150453cf7","tid":1658972,"uid":39643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:33:15.000Z","msg":"1推"},{"pid":"05e9bfbc87daf9050be9cd7f25927268fa3b0518","tid":1658972,"uid":54262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe0c07922f16b47a87d0d81b8d7736e8fe2faf8","tid":1658972,"uid":39643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a02b13c8794ef728a64c98a9e3cc71c820fe7a","tid":1658972,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:55:39.000Z","msg":"唔認同<br />\n<br />\n和理非要掩護勇武 難聽啲講係總係要有人被捕<br />\n因為一個鋤唔入 一個坐十碌<br />\n<br />\n死黑警拉既人係有上限（拉人都要人力物力）你想啲quota用係街坊和理非定勇武到？<br />\n<br />\n即係話如果和理非全部唔黑衫避過針對，勇武一定要黑衫咁就仆街。<br />\n<br />\n和理非幾時可以唔著黑衫？你要街坊裝做哨或做隱藏物資兵既時候"},{"pid":"61f51abda87932d0a62a7dd3b68f1e589c4fb0da","tid":1658972,"uid":274801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T00:58:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"087dd6266d7797b8bbcc89ac714b6980b38bd3e5","tid":1658972,"uid":39643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52db9d6095776bcbdef404542e1e686292e383ab","tid":1658972,"uid":124212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"你訓左幾耐？連點解要BLACK BLOC都唔知？<br />\n一直講緊既係帶衫換<br />\n如果你係覺得着件黑衫冇用既就應該叫和理非帶衫換+full black bloc<br />\n而唔係叫人唔好black bloc"},{"pid":"ba721f8024211453e1812edb6b25ed8d260d648f","tid":1658972,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:31:12.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n辛苦製作，求手足幫推！！！"},{"pid":"9226ea53ecc59416611cf6880b94bc92ffe8f6b1","tid":1658972,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"56cd69c2252d1195d9275a4844dbc6c97fa43d60","tid":1658972,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:23:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> IG &ldquo;bye bye starbucks&rdquo; challenge</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659200</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手推啦各位， 比美心負皮緊呀。"},{"pid":"c35504a6f957e6799b2c536fa06dfdfd790c4007","tid":1658972,"uid":229380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}